Unravelling the potential mechanisms behind hospitalization-associated 
disability in older patients; the Hospital-Associated Disability and impact on 
daily Life (Hospital-ADL) cohort study protocol.

Reichardt LA(1), Aarden JJ(2)(3), van Seben R(4), van der Schaaf M(5)(6), 
Engelbert RH(7)(8), Bosch JA(9), Buurman BM(10)(11); Hospital-ADL study group.

