Recognizing the economic and health-outcome value of early cognitive assessment 
and intervention among its older citizens has guided the Innovative Research 
School in Gerontology of the SD Asfendiyarov Kazakh National Medical University 
to begin the process of establishing its nation's first memory center in Almaty, 
